OL,3,CWhy Afghan refugees are being deported
OL,4,Cfrom Iran to face Taliban rule
OL,6,FMore than a million Afghan refugees
OL,7,Fhave been thrown out of Iran and sent
OL,8,Fback to their own country, where many
OL,9,Fface an uncertain fate. ITV News
OL,10,FInternational Affairs Analyst Rageh
OL,11,FOmaar reports on the world's unseen
OL,12,Frefugee crisis.
OL,14,FIran has hosted millions of Afghan
OL,15,Frefugees for decades.
OL,17,FMany of them have known nothing else,
OL,18,Fother than their lives in Iran.
OL,20,FIn the past few weeks, this all came
OL,21,Fto an end.
