OL,3,CWhy Afghan refugees are being deported
OL,4,Cfrom Iran to face Taliban rule
OL,6,FFirst came the formalities of the
OL,7,Fpaperwork - sending them back to the
OL,8,Fcountry they or their parents fled.
OL,10,FThen came the shock of confronting the
OL,11,Femotional reality of being forcibly
OL,12,Fdeported.
OL,14,FDeportations of illegal migrants are a
OL,15,Fglobal topic - especially in the West.
OL,17,FHowever, the stark number of Afghans
OL,18,Fbeing deported from Iran is startling:
OL,19,F1.5 million sent back so far this year.
OL,21,FSo why is Iran doing this now?
