OL,3,CWhy Afghan refugees are being deported
OL,4,Cfrom Iran to face Taliban rule
OL,6,FIn June this year, Israel conducted a
OL,7,Fdevastating strike on Iran's critical
OL,8,Fmilitary and nuclear facilities and
OL,9,Fassassinated senior Iranian military
OL,10,Fofficials.
OL,12,FIran's suspicion is that Israeli
OL,13,Fintelligence recruited desperate and
OL,14,Fpoor Afghan refugees to be agents, and
OL,15,Fguide Israeli strikes to their targets.
OL,17,FA video produced by the Iranian
OL,18,Fmilitary shows what they say is a
OL,19,Fbunker near a military site - with
OL,20,FAfghans hiding inside it.
