OL,3,CWhy Afghan refugees are being deported
OL,4,Cfrom Iran to face Taliban rule
OL,6,FSo now many, like Maryam, are being
OL,7,Fforced to return to a country ruled by
OL,8,Fthe Taliban.
OL,10,FMayram told ITV News that Iranian
OL,11,Fsecurity forces were not allowing
OL,12,FAfghans to live or work there.
