OL,3,CWhy Afghan refugees are being deported
OL,4,Cfrom Iran to face Taliban rule
OL,6,FHer story is the same for millions of
OL,7,FAfghans, especially women, returning
OL,8,Fto a country where there are virtually
OL,9,Fno humanitarian agencies.
OL,11,FAnd many female returnees are not
OL,12,Fallowed to be educated or go outside
OL,13,Funaccompanied by a male relative.
OL,15,FThis came after years of Western
OL,16,Fintervention in Afghanistan to be rid
OL,17,Fof the Taliban so that refugees could
OL,18,Freturn safely, and not under duress.
